url = git@github.com:GugzSingh/web-server.git

download & install heroku toolbelt

Heroku commands:

heroku create  --> Makes a new heroku app and adds a heroku git remote 
heroku rename <app_name_here>   --> Changes the name of you application 


git add .  --> adds files to commit 
git commit -am "Init repo"  --> commit's files to repository
git push heroku master  --> pushes the application code to the heroku, and you will be able to see your application live on the web 
heroku open  --> Shortcut to open your app on your default browser 
